{"tid":18308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港都有分店】《舌尖上的中國2》浙火鍋名店　被揭用二手回收油受查","createTime":"2016-12-02T08:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T10:04:45.000Z","uid":22680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de00887da3589ae2c6a81059a3fa3d4d2b3ed58c","tid":18308,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161201/s00004/1480588971678SL4_0C1C2DE54606289E212D882E955ACDD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161201%2Fs00004%2F1480588971678SL4_0C1C2DE54606289E212D882E955ACDD6.jpg&h=03f452ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少港人喜歡北上打邊爐，不過浙江溫洲及瑞安有多間著名火鍋店涉使用二手回收油被當局調查，當中更有曾在《舌尖上的中國2》亮相的渝味曉宇火鍋，該火鍋店更今年10月進軍香港，在銅鑼灣開設分店。<br />\n<br />\n當局繼查獲溫州「大龍燚」、「萬德府」等知名火鍋店涉用回收油外，瑞安市公安和市監部門近日相繼查獲8家火鍋店涉用回收油，目前已有24名涉案人士被警方拘捕，涉案的火鍋店包括渝味曉宇火鍋、柒口鍋成都火鍋、千椒百味火鍋、重慶名將火鍋店、阿雲重慶老火鍋、塘下重慶八旺串串香火鍋、塘下朝天門火鍋及塘下重慶老火鍋，其中5間已暫時停業。<br />\n瑞安市市場監督管理局副局長、瑞安市食安辦專職副主任沈安剛表示，店家回收二手油的手法大致相同，先回收顧客食用後的火鍋底料油，混合新油再加工，最後再供顧客食用。公安機關目前以涉嫌非法生產、銷售有毒、有害食品罪拘捕24名疑犯，市監部門責令8間涉案火鍋店停業整頓，案件正在進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00004/1480586374664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00004%2F1480586374664&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BPxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=df73acfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00004%2F1480586374664&h=10076c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00004/1480586374664</a><br />\n<br />\n之前仲見到班傻鳩話要去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c139b683b03e43df90f4e99ff42ab864d8738d99","tid":18308,"uid":27024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"唔係用二手油, 你班仆街點會食得咁滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452a36c3cb2beb18219f80df6478bf1ccf27c962","tid":18308,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係用二手油, 你班仆街點會食得咁滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 👍🏻"},{"pid":"a87ac56bff34dd6cf1d7eb468bb89d5fa11afbd5","tid":18308,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626a79d9eccfff0b1ee70e6521c0be2b385bf4ba","tid":18308,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"仆街了 , 黎緊去重慶仲想試下添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}